en_260170_0	“Cold Pursuit” is an upcoming American action film directed by Hans Petter Moland from a screenplay by Frank Baldwin.
en_260170_1	It stars Liam Neeson, Laura Dern, Emmy Rossum, William Forsythe and Tom Bateman.
en_260170_2	Nels Coxman’s quiet life as a snowplow driver in a glitzy Rocky Mountains resort town where he was just awarded Citizen of the Year is disrupted when his beloved son is murdered under mysterious circumstances.
en_260170_3	His search for the cause turns into a quest for revenge against a psychotic drug lord named Viking.
en_260170_4	The film is scheduled to be released in the United States this Friday by Summit Entertainment.
